@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Us";
}

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>@ViewData["Title"]</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            color: #333;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        h1, h2, h3 {
            color: #007bff;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }

        p {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        ul {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        li {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        footer {
            margin-top: 50px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #777;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container mt-5">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-8 offset-md-2">
                <h1 class="text-center">Agri-Energy Connect</h1>
                <h2 class="text-center">Bridging Agriculture and Green Energy</h2>
                <p class="lead text-center">
                    At Agri-Energy Connect, we are dedicated to fostering a sustainable future by seamlessly integrating agriculture with innovative green energy solutions. Our digital ecosystem serves as a collaborative hub for farmers, energy experts, and enthusiasts to share knowledge, resources, and drive innovation in sustainable farming and renewable energy.
                </p>

                <h3>Our Vision</h3>
                <p>
                    To create a thriving digital space that empowers the agricultural community to embrace renewable energy, enhancing productivity and environmental stewardship.
                </p>

                <h3>Our Platform’s Key Features</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Sustainable Farming Hub:</strong> Access a wealth of resources on organic farming, water conservation, and soil health. Engage in vibrant forums to exchange ideas and collaborate on eco-friendly farming practices.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Green Energy Marketplace:</strong> Discover and compare cutting-edge green energy products tailored for agricultural needs. Connect with technology providers offering solutions like solar-powered irrigation and biogas systems.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Educational Resources:</strong> Learn through online courses and workshops about the integration of green technologies in agriculture, focusing on the benefits and practical implementation of renewable energy on farms.
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Collaboration Opportunities:</strong> Join forces with experts to propose and develop joint projects. Explore funding options to support your green initiatives in agriculture.
                    </li>
                </ul>

                <h3>Our Commitment</h3>
                <p>
                    We are committed to providing a user-friendly and secure platform that caters to a diverse audience, ensuring data privacy and fostering real-time collaboration and innovation.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Join us at Agri-Energy Connect, where agriculture meets green energy for a sustainable tomorrow.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="text-center">Effective Date: [10/05/2024]</footer>

</body>
</html>



